The pandemic has brought many things to a standstill. However, with everything being online, schools have faced difficulty tracking the attendance of its employees and students. We made an attempt to tackle this problem. 

The project is implemented with a MySQL DataBase using Python Flask. On one end, the user checks in with their information to a class. On the other end the professor gets the information on who checked in. This program was implemented using Python Flask, MySQL, and Hypertext PreProcessor(PHP).  
